{
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_275": "你知道那是什么\n感觉吗？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_283": "你知道那种...\n被抛弃的感觉吗？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_291": "就同在黑暗中徘徊，\n感到恐惧，与迷茫...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_299": "留下一个又一个\n疑问...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_304": "“为什么我会被抛弃？\n我是做错了什么？”",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_310": "“我...是不是\n还不够好？”",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_316": "我们曾是最好的朋友。\n你总是很尊重我。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_322": "所以告诉我为什么？\n你至少也要给我一个\n理由吧？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_328": "能回答我一下吗，\nKris？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_334": "或者... 你还是想对我\n隐瞒真相？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_340": "我已经竭尽所能，\n做了一切我该做的事。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_346": "我竭尽全力———只为\n成为你心目中的\n完美人物。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_352": "我多么希望，自己能\n成为那个给予你救赎\n带你走出阴霾的人...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_358": "成为那个能够激励你\n坚持下去的人！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_364": "说起来也挺有意思，\n是吧？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_370": "我尝试带你走出那片\n阴影，而你却卸磨杀驴，\n将我抛弃在那里？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_376": "不过也好，我在\n那里找到了一个家。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_382": "一个不会有人在我\n背后捅刀子的家！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_388": "当你回来的时候，\n我满脑子想的就是\n要找到你。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_394": "一是为了复仇，\n但也仅此而已。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_400": "真正的目的，是我一直\n想要知道我到底哪里\n做错了。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_406": "但要是你不能，\n或者不愿意告诉我\n答案...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_412": "那么，这样也就\n没有意义了。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_kf_Draw_73_418": "所以，永别吧，\nKris。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_kreid_c3_Draw_73_250": "然而...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_kreid_c3_Draw_73_258": "你... 你...！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_primflower_Draw_73_494": "你想买\n什么呢？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_primflower_Draw_73_539": "好可惜\n呢...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_primflower_Draw_73_525": "算我请的\n好啦~",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_primflower_Draw_73_532": "谢谢了，\n哈哈~",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_primflower_Draw_73_75": "聊天很适合\n用来打发\n时间呢~",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_263": "很抱歉节目会以这种\n方式结束，但我们\n还会重新上映的。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_274": "我们之前就重启过\n它，所以再重启一次\n也情有可原。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_285": "*嗞*嘿嘿嘿女士们，\n先生们，还有这些不可\n名状的生物们！*嗞*",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_296": "*嗞*你们的主持人\n渴望着暴力。*嗞*",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_307": "幸运的是，光之民\n将不会只是个\n特邀嘉宾。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_318": "我们将会邀请更多\n光之民来到节目常驻！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_331": "谁会听你的啊！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_333": "谁...（咳）\n会听你的！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_345": "比如Toriel，大概吧？\n但主要是那个幽灵，\n既易受影响，\n也易被操纵...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_356": "简直就是一个\n完美的电视明星！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_380": "你知道Mike会\n怎么想吗？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_382": "（...）",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_394": "我弟弟也许会\n感情用事，不过他\n最终会理解的。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_418": "理解啥？\n把光之民永远困在\n这里吗？！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_420": "（...）",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_434": "额... 对？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_436": "在你们提问之前... 对。\n我们会把光之民永远\n困在这里。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_459": "你们这些孩子会觉得\n我是个坏人，但你们\n错了。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_489": "我所做的一切\n都是合情合理。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_511": "包括贿赂我的敌人，\n强迫我的员工\n在节假日加班...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_522": "但这一切都只是为了\n促进这个世界的繁荣！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_544": "我的人民需要\n一片指路的明光。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_566": "而你们却一次又\n一次让我们失望...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_577": "所以我们只能去往\n其他地方找到那片\n光。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_599": "同时这个责任，\n让人们重新绽放\n笑容的责任，\n就由我来担当。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_610": "虽然肯定会有人\n因此牺牲，不过从\n长远来看，牺牲是\n值得的。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_632": "午夜帮的人是对的...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_664": "你跟他们一样\n也是一名罪犯！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_666": "你跟他们一样\n也是一名罪犯！（咳）",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_679": "错误。我所做的\n一切都并非犯罪。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_691": "*嗞*没错！\n她依法享有免受任何\n不当行为指控的权利！\n*嗞*",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_703": "要让事情回到正轨，\n需要付出大量的努力。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_715": "我忍受那些黑影中的\n混混已经很长时间了...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_727": "而你们却在我的城市里\n到处散播错误的观念，\n误导了人们的思想。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_750": "...造成那么多的\n混乱纷扰，让其\n涌向我的面前。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_762": "要把这一切处理好\n我得喝多少咖啡啊。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_785": "不过综合考虑各种\n因素，我对未来还是\n持乐观态度。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_797": "你们的那些敌对无礼\n的行为在我看来，\n只是一颗小小的\n绊脚石罢了。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_809": "虽然是一颗\n能让人耗尽所有\n精力的绊脚石。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_832": "其实也就是搞\n几次重播然后插播\n几条广告的事。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_861": "毕竟人们只愿意相信\n电视上的内容，尤其是\n有Mike的内容。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_873": "凭借他的声音和我\n敏锐的目光，\n一切都会平安无事。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_885": "广播世界将再次成为\n充满活力的天堂！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_910": "你不是认真的吧。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_927": "MIKE，这玩意怎么\n设置成困难模式啊！？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_929": "太Tenna棒了！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_941": "...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_954": "*嗞*姐姐，\n我还没设置成\n“困难模式”呢。\n*嗞*",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_956": "*嗞*姐姐，\n这笑话太烂了。\n*嗞*",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_970": "*嗞*我不觉得\n他们能躲过所有的 ",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_972": "*嗞*我跟你说话\n你有没有在 ",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_996": " ",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_912": "我猜你会说...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_1013": "不过，关于我的那些\n宏大计划（就是清理\n你们那堆烂摊子的\n计划），就先不提了。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_1025": "这简直太占\n我原本打算用来\n教训你的时间了...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sio_Draw_73_1048": "所以，就是，\n请安心挨揍？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3484": "我接收到了来自\n外界的信号号号号号号",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3492": "所有那些充满哀伤的\n电话，都在诉说着希望\n生活能有所不同...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3500": "我理解你的犹豫不决，\n但为什么就让我在这\n干等着呢呢呢呢呢呢呢？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3508": "你我都明白，在这\n令人厌恶的提线上起舞，\n注定要与一些风景擦肩。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3516": "哈哈哈！我们都成为了\n如何可爱愚蠢的木偶啊！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3523": "如果我无法说服\n你退出...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3530": "也许让你更熟悉的人\n来说服你比较合适？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3537": "告诉我我我我我我",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3544": "在战胜了疯狂的小丑与\n卑鄙的骗子之后，你真的\n想要停止追寻那个信号吗？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3552": "就这样不甘心的活着，\n任由甜言蜜语伴你耳畔？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3560": "我知道听到这些可能\n会让你很难受，但请不要\n过于沮丧！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3568": "当我悲伤时，我喜欢\n播放我最喜欢的\n歌曲曲曲曲曲曲曲",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3576": "看看生活将会变得\n多么光明！\n来一片吧...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3584": "在这样一个让我们\n陷入沉寂的世界里，\n我会与你并肩而立！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3591": "我们都不用再\n孤独一人了！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3598": "你不必再像个傻子一样，\n呆呆地望着那\n虚假的天空...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3605": "看到你那破碎的心灵\n竟以一只#$%!的猫咪\n的形象呈现出来来来来",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3612": "哎呀呀，你最近可真是\n受欢迎啊，Kris！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3620": "有好多人想跟你\n通电话呢呢呢呢呢！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3627": "你知道吗，我一直觉得\n我有很多话想说...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3634": "当我听到那些电话时，\n我才意识到我的话\n毫无意义。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3641": "跟你说吧，讲一堆\n废话还不如无所事事\n地躺着有趣呢。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3648": "一想到那些，我的\n整个身体就会\n恶心地嗡嗡作响！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3655": "城市兴衰更迭，\n人们或登场或\n退场场场场场场场",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3663": "...但一切都不会\n改变。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3670": "一切都不重要... \n除了...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3677": "除了... 我们 ",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3691": "           ",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3715": "额，等一下...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3723": "   ",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3742": "好像打错电话了。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3753": "...除非我们侧耳\n聆听天堂的声音，\n否则一切都毫无意义。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3762": "哈哈哈！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3770": "看看我在短短一天内\n所取得的成就\n吧吧吧吧吧吧吧",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3777": "没人能将我从这种高度\n上拉下来，没人能做到。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3784": "它越来越近了...\n你听到了吗？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3793": "那是我自由的信号！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_battle_sof_Draw_73_3795": "EX静电共鸣已经降临！",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_40": "我们又来到了这里。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_46": "Ralsei说的对，\n我们确实取得了很大进展。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_52": "我想知道，我们还需要\n经历这样的冒险多少次...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_58": "感觉每一次冒险的\n规模都变得越来越大。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_64": "我觉得... 这会不会\n让我们三个有点应付不来呢？",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_71": "...",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_78": "算了，先不想这个了。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_85": "该你上了，Kris。",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_falsefountain_text_Draw_73_92": "（就好像你的灵魂都在\n闪耀着光芒...）",
    "battle_gml_Object_obj_primflower_Draw_73_546": "真不巧呢..."
}
